sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Caller
  participant Broker as Inquiry broker
  participant GraphA as Graph execution A
  participant Task
  participant Signal as Signal broker
  participant GraphB as Graph execution B
  participant Evidence

  Caller->>Broker: inquire under new trace
  Broker->>GraphA: start responder graph
  GraphA->>Task: execute awaited task relationship
  Task-->>GraphA: terminal business context
  Task-->>Signal: emit detached signal with trace identity
  GraphA->>Evidence: graph and composition evidence
  GraphA-->>Broker: deterministic conclusion
  Broker-->>Caller: result or explicit failure
  Signal->>GraphB: start new graph execution under same trace
  GraphB->>Evidence: causally linked continuation evidence
  Note over GraphA,GraphB: Graph A completion does not wait for Graph B, but both remain interpretable under one trace.
